{"tid":946434,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱見到個仲簡單嘅贏國翻牆工具 - Brook","createTime":"2018-12-18T13:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T10:29:48.000Z","uid":17738,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4bc13dcc2dfa91ded52e36c66bd207bcb2538370","tid":946434,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T13:41:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://github.com/txthinking/brook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Ftxthinking%2Fbrook&d=qAjeUnq431rM%2BBBwyK7HkdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=2c463aab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/txthinking/brook</a><br />\n<br />\n喺Cygwin運行或者windows 10嘅cmd.exe運行都得，不過Cygwin有nohup 命令，退出咗shell都仲運行，cmd.exe就要開住<br />\n<br />\n非常簡單，我部windows嘅cygwin執行，喺router開個port forword轉去windows notebook就得<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">nohup ./brook_windows_amd64.exe server -l :9999 -p YourPasswordHere &amp;</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n去iOS app Store search Brook，安裝下載之後輸入相應資料OK，好似內建PAC，閂咗WiFi去 <a href=\"https://check.torproject.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcheck.torproject.org&d=qAjeUnq431rM%2BBBwyK7HkdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=2bfdbdf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://check.torproject.org</a> 就係寬頻IP，去 <a href=\"https://ifconfig.co\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fifconfig.co&d=qAjeUnq431rM%2BBBwyK7HkdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=eaca91c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ifconfig.co</a> 就係流動網絡供應商IP<br />\n<br />\n不過Android 嘅client 連唔到網站，原因不明，睇完nohup.out同項目issues都係搞唔掂"},{"pid":"a9e84aaa4f3b557812131c87265ce471bfed5856","tid":946434,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T13:45:42.000Z","msg":"暫時未喺贏國測試，加密方式似乎fix咗係aes-256-cfb，冇得用chacha20-ietf-poly1305呢類加密"},{"pid":"167b586fbaff196bb2750e53bec8b5dfc2170901","tid":946434,"uid":95172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:07:48.000Z","msg":"已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de9a89c1a5e1149537f2215a1e799628e5255f2b","tid":946434,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:10:14.000Z","msg":"Twitter啲友話得，要親自實地試驗先知，但真係簡單到冇難度，完全唔需要任何電腦起server知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1dc52763c57b16ba1ebad7fd599c1a116965f83","tid":946434,"uid":1402,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T22:19:04.000Z","msg":"又係用go寫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14552b627d0a8964c16727f5e06a7cb0d0d36196","tid":946434,"uid":72667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T01:49:56.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"7abdbdc624742cabcf35afb00920415bee72fbfa","tid":946434,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9e84aaa4f3b557812131c87265ce471bfed5856","tid":946434,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T13:45:42.000Z","msg":"暫時未喺贏國測試，加密方式似乎fix咗係aes-256-cfb，冇得用chacha20-ietf-poly1305呢類加密"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:04:20.000Z","msg":"雖然唔識go，不過呢段code估應該係<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">func NewCipherConn(c net.Conn, key []byte, iv []byte) (*CipherConn, error) {\n\tif len(iv) != aes.BlockSize {\n\t\treturn nil, errors.New(&rdquo;Invalid IV length&ldquo;)\n\t}\n\tblock, err := aes.NewCipher(x.AESMake256Key(key))\n\tif err != nil {\n\t\treturn nil, err\n\t}\n\treturn &amp;CipherConn{\n\t\tc: c,\n\t\tsr: cipher.StreamReader{\n\t\t\tS: cipher.NewCFBDecrypter(block, iv),\n\t\t\tR: c,\n\t\t},\n\t\tsw: cipher.StreamWriter{\n\t\t\tS: cipher.NewCFBEncrypter(block, iv),\n\t\t\tW: c,\n\t\t},\n\t}, nil\n}</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3a0b3c7f60be01a6f60c9e2efa38d4447d8dcbfc","tid":946434,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"今晚係屋企試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"142919551562629f4cd422b4edb1686c567